metadata.name: Fall Reflections
metadata.description:
This is a picture of the Ausable River, in the Adirondack Park of New York State. It is just below a historic covered bridge. The picture was taken in the fall just as the colors were nearing their peak colors. The reflections on the very still Ausable River were astounding!

4696 x 7080, Canon EOS 90D, F/13, 1/40 sec., ISO-100, 16mm
